ta})$, for any\n$\\delta>0$. We implement our method on several examples including Bayesian\ninverse problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Mar 2022 17:30:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 12:20:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
