namical states. Finally, by increasing the network\nsize, the robustness of the chimera is also inspected and we find that the\nchimera state is robust even in networks of larger sizes. We also show the\ngenerality of the above results in the related phase reduced model as well as\nin other coupled models such as the globally coupled van der Pol and R\\\"ossler\noscillators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Mar 2022 17:44:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
