hnical and institutional features relate to each other, and\nprovide complementary views into the progress of the ASF's OSS projects.\nRefining these combined analyses can help provide a more precise understanding\nof the synchronization between the evolution of institutional governance and\norganizational structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2022 05:35:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-08"}
