 to distinguish between the different states. Our model\nresults suggest that short range packing is likely to be a key regulator of the\nstability and size distribution of biological rafts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2022 10:42:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 Jul 2022 16:34:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 5 Mar 2023 14:33:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-07"}
