which the observational eccentricities, $e_b$\nand $e_c$, are favored as long as $e_d\\approx 0$. With the aim to obtain an\noptimum deduction of the orbital elements, this study showcases the need for\ndynamical analyses based on periodic orbits performed in parallel to the\nfitting processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2022 12:56:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 17:07:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
